{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset is based on MRBench, a curated collection of math-focused educational dialogues designed for evaluating feedback quality in instructional settings (Maurya et al., 2025).",
    "It includes dialogues drawn from two publicly available sources: MathDial (Macina et al., 2023) and Bridge (Wang et al., 2024).",
    "Each instance comprises a multi-turn conversation between a student and an AI tutor, a final student question or statement, and multiple candidate tutor responses.",
    "The task is to classify each response along the four instructional dimensions, using a three-way labeling scheme: Yes, To some extent, and No.",
    "The shared task organizers provide a labeled development set with expert annotations for training and validation."
  ]
}